caption.p:
Heatmap showing relative levels of small metabolic compounds in TB patients (TB
active
) and latently infected individuals (TST+). For purposes of illustration, 10 profiles from each group were randomly assigned to a test set, and calculations were repeated for the remaining training set. Left, training-set levels; only 50 compounds selected by variable importance from the RF model were chosen. Right, test-set levels; all test set samples were correctly assigned to a study class.
